Hello! Welcome to West Barnstable Horse Hides, the finest bowling alley in town. My name is Alex. How may I assist you today? Could I have your name, please?

Hi Alex, my name is Jamie. I'm calling about a charge on my billing statement that I need some clarification on.

Thank you, Jamie. I'd be happy to help with that. To pull up your account, could I have your billing account number, please?

Certainly, it's zero zero zero one two three four five six.

Great, let me verify this information. May I also have the last four digits of the phone number associated with your account?

Sure, it's seven eight nine zero.

Thank you, Jamie. I've pulled up your account. I see the charge you're referring to. It looks like it was for a group event on the weekend. Does that sound correct?

Yes, that does make sense. I just wanted to confirm that was what the charge was for.

I'm glad we could clarify that. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

No, that should be all for now. Thank you!

You're welcome, Jamie. Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
